Class Inventory

java.lang.Object
com.example.inventory_manage_application.Model.Inventory
public class Inventory extends Object
An inventory class that generate lists. It allows you to add listeners that will be notified, when an item is added or removed from the list. The FXCollections class is a utility class that provides various static methods for creating and modifying observable lists.The observableArrayList method creates a new observable list that is backed by an array
